      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "AirdPro is a GUI client for vendor file converting written in C#... Aird is designed to become a computing-oriented data format with high scalability, compression rate, and fast decoding speed... Aird merely takes 33% decoding time compared with Zlib... m/z data size is about 55% lower in Aird average.",
